Class MgEnvelope

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.osgeo.mapguide.MgObject

        • org.osgeo.mapguide.MgGuardDisposable
          • org.osgeo.mapguide.MgSerializable
            • org.osgeo.mapguide.MgEnvelope

  • public class MgEnvelope
extends MgSerializable
    MgEnvelope represents a bounding box defined in terms of a lower left coordinate and an upper right coordinate.
